        <item>
            <title>【教學】幫 iPhone 清除 IG、FB 無用垃圾　實試釋放手機 16 GB 儲存容量</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/iphone-clear-cache-2024/tips-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-clear-cache-2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/iphone-clear-cache-2024/tips-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 11:30:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[實用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Facebook]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[instagram]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1254150</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>相信大部份讀者每日也會上 Instagram、Facebook，小編自己也是 Instagram 重度成癮者，經常會在 Instagram 和朋友互相傳送迷因。長久下來，Instagram 和 Facebook 的 cache 會佔用手提電話大量儲存空間。此時就需要清理 Instagram 及 Facebook 的暫存數據。以下小編會利用 iOS 裝置示範如何清除 Instagram、Facebook 的暫存數據，拿回本身屬於你的儲存空間。</p><p>如果你想查看你的 Instagram、Facebook 佔用多少儲存位置的話，可以進入「設定」，然後點擊「一般」，選擇「iPhone 儲存空間」。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254163" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-2-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-2-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-2.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲進入設定</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254164" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_1-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_1-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_1.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「一般」</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254165" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_2-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_2-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_2.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「iPhone 儲存空間」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254205" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-7-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-7-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-7.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲上下滑動，尋找你想知道佔用多少空間的應用程式</p><p>在清理快取前，先看看小編 Instagram 和 Facebook 佔用了多少儲存空間。不檢查猶自可，一看才發現這 2 個應用程式居然佔用了近 17 GB 儲存。此時我們可以按「刪除 App」來移除應用程式，iPhone 就會清理應用程式佔用的空間，之後再重新下載即可使用，無須重新登入。如果你的 Facebook 帳户連結了 Instagram，那麼你登入其中一個社交平台後，系統就會自動幫你登入另一個。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254167" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-4-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-4-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-4.jpg 831w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲難以想像原來這兩個應用程式佔用了這麼多空間</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254172" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-5.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲刪除後重新安裝 Instagram 及 Facebook</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_3-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_3-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_3-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_3.png 591w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲重新安裝後，可發現之前的登入資料仍然存在。你不需再次登入，只要點擊你的 Instagram 帳户即可</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254179" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_4-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_4-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_4.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Facebook 亦可以在你重新安裝後，一鍵直接登入</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-6-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-6-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-6.jpg 831w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲現在 2 個應用程式佔用的空間大幅下降至約 100 MB ，節省了不少儲存空間</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254193" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_5-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_5-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_5.jpg 831w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小編本來只有 87.52 GB 空間（紅框示），重新安裝 IG FB 後儲存多了近 16 GB，<br />
提升至 103.37 GB（綠框示）</p><h2>總結：釋放空間必備招式　不用再擔心電話無位</h2><p>小編先前因為電話儲存空間不足，所以才換了新電話，現在學懂這一招後，馬上就騰空了不少儲存空間。如果你的電話也有儲存空間不足的問題，可以嘗試刪除 Facebook、Instagram 然後重新安裝，這樣應該可以騰空不少位置。不過要留意不是每一個應用程式刪除後重新安裝都可自動登入，小編試過刪除 Telegram 後重新安裝，Telegram 會要求小編自行重新登入，因此刪除 Instagram 和 Facebook 以外的應用程式前，請先找個安全位置記下帳户密碼等資訊，並確保你有方法再次登入該程式。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/08/how-to-use-gemini-on-ios-and-android-devices/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】iPhone 都用到 Gemini　教你如何在 Android 和 iOS 裝置上使用</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/02/ios18-features-that-most-people-missed/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】iOS 18 大部分人可能錯過的新功能　留言信箱廣東話變文字 + 音量鍵電源鍵新操作動畫</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/24/huawei-pura70-ultra-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Huawei Pura70 Ultra　由 iOS / Android 轉會 HMS 不影響生活教學 + 實試</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/iphone-clear-cache-2024/tips-2/">【教學】幫 iPhone 清除 IG、FB 無用垃圾　實試釋放手機 16 GB 儲存容量</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
